        "type": "jwt",
        "label": "Vonage application JWT",
        "generateUrl": "https://dashboard.nexmo.com/applications",
        "setup": "Create a Vonage application in the [Applications](https://dashboard.nexmo.com/applications) area of the dashboard, generate or download its private key, and use the resulting `APP_ID` + private key to mint JWTs. The docs note you can also use the Vonage CLI or SDKs to generate the JWT. Keep the private key secure; it is only available when the application is created or when keys are regenerated.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
